 	help
 	  This option adds the `SNPT' and `DNPT' target, which perform
 	  stateless IPv6-to-IPv6 Network Prefix Translation per RFC 6296.
 
 	  To compile it as a module, choose M here.  If unsure, say N.
 
-endif # IP6_NF_NAT
-
 endif # IP6_NF_IPTABLES
 endmenu
 
